    • initialize

      public void initialize(URL url, ResourceBundle resourceBundle)
      Initializes this controller. Check for the presence of a Part to be modified in the selectedPart static Part variable, and renders the associated view as the "Modify Part" screen if such data is available, pre-populating the Part's data into the appropriate text fields for editing.
